snippet.title: ARTNETWORKTV
snippet.description: Envisioning the Earth as a work of Art, ArtNetworkTV was established to express the worldview that perceives life on Earth and the Cosmos as an evolving creative Consciousness. Our mission is to produce and curate documentaries that promote the understanding of the arts, cultures, and traditions of people from all over the world. You are welcome to watch the videos, subscribe to support our work, receive updates and offer your comments and suggestions.  ❤
